rows.label: tev025602_MSG0001
rows.name:
Oh, are you here to get some advice from Hope?
So sorry, but we're booked solid for the day.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025602_MSG0002
rows.name:
Hope would work right through dawn if no one
stopped her, so I have to step in and draw the line.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025602_MSG0003
rows.name:
No hard feelings, okay? Come back the next time we
start taking appointments and I promise we'll take
good care of you.[ST:wait ]
